    Fix CVE-2021-37650

    Cherry-pick upstream commit e0b6e58c3.

    Fix segfault/heap buffer overflow in `{Experimental,}DatasetToTFRecord` where
    dataset is numeric.

    Code assumes only strings inputs and then interprets numbers as valid
    `tstring`s. Then, when trying to compute the CRC of the record this results in
    heap buffer overflow.

