    Setting TF_DEVICE_MIN_SYS_MEMORY_IN_MB will force TF to leave the specified
    number of MB un-allocated.

    Also, removed the 6% of memory reservation in favor of a fixed default sysmem
    reservation of 800 MB for Volta and later and of 300MB for Pascal and eariler.
